        "text": "EXTENSION HOST SERVICES\n\nThis column is the backend brain:\n- path-resolver: resolves import specifiers to absolute file paths (handles aliases, barrel files)\n- symbol-extractor: uses TypeScript AST to extract functions, classes, types from files\n- file-reader: reads file from disk + runs symbol extraction\n- import-scanner: parses import statements from source code\n- category-filter: classifies imports as source/styles/data\n- dependency-graph: orchestrates the full dependency tree expansion"
      }
